data.description: Priced to Sell, Great Value for this 1 Bedroom 1 Bathroom Condo on the Top Floor with gorgeous views.  Newer Luxury Vinyl Flooring in the main living area.  Extended Living has a Murphy Bed for your guest.  Brand new windows in the back of the unit, all windows are impact resistant.  A/C is 2 years old and the Hot Water Heater is 1 year old.  Updated switches through the condo. Move to Seven Lakes and enjoy the 55 + Active Adult Community with bundled golf, Condo fees cover your internet service, cable, water, sewer, trash removal, lawn maintenance and all amenities.  Amenities are 6 heated pools, 6 tennis courts, pickle ball courts, shuffleboard, bocce ball, card clubs, exercise room, hobby/craft room and large auditorium that host variety of entertainment.  Tee Room Restaurant On-Site for your enjoyment and convenience.   24-hour manned guard gat.  Seven Lakes Community is located minutes from Fort Myers Beach, Sanibel-Captivia Island.  Directly across the street is Bell Tower Shops and Restaurants.  Conveniently close to RSW International Airport too.
